### Problem Statement

Food wastage has become a huge issue due to the concerning amount of its increasing rate each year.Therefore, it's important to analyse this issue.

### Questions

- What are the trends of the change in the food loss percentage from the year 2000 until 2021?
- What is the total food wastage caused by households, food services, and retails in a region or country?
- At which stage does the food waste occur the most?

---

### Solution

Food Wastage is a complex issue and has been a serious problem globally. Hence, this project will help to visualize the data regarding food wastage to raise awareness regarding the gravity it holds.

### Objective

- To identify patterns of food waste trends from 2000 to 2021 globally.
- To visualize the data of food waste according to the food chain stages.
- To display the estimation of food waste according to household, food service and retail categories.

---

### Features that we have acquired from the dataset
- Estimated Food Waste over the Years, 2000-2021.		
- Estimated Food Waste by Region and Industries.		
- Estimated Food Waste by the Stage for all Countries.

Food Counsel Shiny Application is available here:
[https://azrulhaikal.shinyapps.io/Food_Counsel/](https://azrulhaikal.shinyapps.io/Food_Counsel/)

The dataset we used in this project is available at:  
[https://www.unep.org/resources/report/unep-food-waste-index-report-2021](https://www.unep.org/resources/report/unep-food-waste-index-report-2021)  
[https://www.fao.org/platform-food-loss-waste/flw-data/en/](https://www.fao.org/platform-food-loss-waste/flw-data/en/)

Source code for this application is available on Github:
[https://github.com/zrlxkai/FoodCounsel](https://github.com/zrlxkai/FoodCounsel)

